rows.label: qev092504_MSG0001
rows.name: At first glance, her design looks like complete fantasy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092504_MSG0002
rows.name:
But that's the thingâ€”making the impossible real like this
schematic does is every engineer's fantasy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092504_MSG0003
rows.name: Heh. Genetics are a scary thing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092504_MSG0004
rows.name:
I've only had designs this insane shoved at me once
before, and I wasn't able to make them happen then.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092504_MSG0005
rows.name:
This time, though, I swear to make these a reality.
You bring the materials, I'll see the rest gets done.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092504_MSG0006
rows.name:
Don't worry, she'll fly. I can guarantee that as chief
engineer of Sakuraba Industries.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092504_MSG0007
rows.name:
You've got nothing to worry about. Now go take that
little genius's dreams and deliver them to the clouds.[ST:wait ]
